formula: a(n) = sum of the n-th row of A186715.
xref: Connected regular graphs of any degree with girth at least g: A005177 (g=3), A186724 (g=4), this sequence (g=5), A186726 (g=6), A186727 (g=7), A186728 (g=8), A186729 (g=9).
Connected k-regular simple graphs with girth at least 5: this sequence (all k), A186715 (triangle); A185115 (k=2), A014372 (k=3), A058343 (k=4), A205295 (k=5).
